Description
search for verses that contains all of the search words.
search for verses that contains all of the search phrase.
search for verses that contains any of the search words.
search for verses not contained of the search words. Without can not be used by it self, meaning that it has to be minimum one more condition included (all/at least one,etc)
search for verses that contains words that start with the search words
search for verses that contains words that similar in spelling to the search words.
set the max displaying in one page.
set searching range
Example
"fish bread" will search for verses that contains fish AND bread in minimum 1 bible version
"fish bread" will search for verses that contains "fish bread" in minimum 1 bible version
"fish bread" will search for verses that contains fish OR bread in minumum 1 bible version
all: "fish", without: "bread", will search for verses that contains "fish" but NOT "bread"
"fis" will search for verses that contains words start with "fis", the result will be "fish", "fishing", "fisherman", etc
"fish" will search verses that contain words which has similar spelling with fish. The result: "dish",etc
"20" will set displaying max to 20 per page
"All Bible", "Old Testament", "New Testament"
